[4] Czech Republic: 1st case ex Germany
Date: Wed 1 Jun 2011
Source: Deutsche Presse Agentur (DPA) [edited]
http://www.monstersandcritics.com/news/health/news/article_1642821.php/First-confirmed-EHEC-case-in-the-Czech-Republic


Czech health officials on Tue 31 May 2011, confirmed the country's
1st case of an _E. coli_ epidemic that has been radiating from Germany
over the last week.

The American tourist had just arrived in the Central European country
after a trip to northern Germany, where she had eaten vegetable
salads. She is being treated in the infectious disease ward of a
Prague hospital.

